data.title: JAMES NEWTON HOWARD & FRIENDS DIRECT TO DISK Audiophile LP SHEFIELD LAB 23 TOTO
data.meta_description: check the value of your vinyl records by searching our archive
data.text:
JAMES NEWTON HOWARD & FRIENDS rare DIRECT TO DISK Limited Edition LP from 1983 (SHEFFIELD LAB Lab 23). Very sought after by Audiophiles due to amazing sonics. With original inserts. The record was pressed on audiophile quality virgin vinyl and is Translucent when held against a light source (similar to QUIEX II and MFSL LPs). Featuring some members of TOTO: DAVID PAICH, STEVE PORCARO, JEFF PORCARO, and JOE PORCARO. Sleeve is EX. Record is Near Mint.

I offer combined shipping discount. If you buy multiple items you save a lot on shipping. If possible please wait for me to send you invoice if you buy more than one item.
